r>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-Th%E1%BA%ADn/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1-l%E1%BB%AF-ho%C3%A0i-ng%C3%A2m/poem-QwHBlDHxHjNmmwiMhPsXpg">Thu dạ lữ hoài ngâm - 秋夜旅懷吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-Th%E1%BA%ADn/author-Hrw_uUvQJ05Gjc8O2RkROQ">Đinh Nhật Thận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kim-%C4%90%E1%BB%8Ba-T%E1%BA%A1ng/T%E1%BB%91ng-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-t%E1%BB%AD-h%E1%BA%A1-s%C6%A1n/poem-PQqViutVbAvRrO0S68DtDw">Tống đồng tử hạ sơn - 送童子下山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kim-%C4%90%E1%BB%8Ba-T%E1%BA%A1ng/author-aPv2VEhn9m7CEBXzuAiuWQ">Kim Địa Tạng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-H%E1%BB%8Dc-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/V%C4%83n-chung/poem-sMXrZTDvW5uflSvv6NTMXQ">Văn chung - 聞鐘</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-H%E1%BB%8Dc-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-mKbTcUGUYHdlKk9fAVqOUw">Viên Học thiền sư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/Xu%C3%A2n-d%E1%BA%A1-t%E1%BB%A9c-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-6JcqIMHQLopeSGmQ1e3oRA">Xuân dạ tức sự - 春夜即事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br></div>	</div>
